   {
      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "A personal signet requires a personal signet challenge. The signet network magic is defined by the signet challenge. Therefore, network magic will be different for each personal signet.\r\nThe signet commitment included in the coinbase transaction includes the signet header (magic). It is verified with the following code.\r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/95ea54ba089610019a74c1176a2c7c0dba144b1c/src/signet.cpp#L41\r\nIf SIGNET_HEADER is specified as a constant on the 26th line, the personal signet block will be rejected.\r\nIn the case of bitcoin v0.21.0, personal signet will not start just by modifying signet.cpp.",
      "created_at" : "2021-01-22T00:46:47Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/20970#issuecomment-765036745",
      "id" : 765036745,
      "issue_url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/20970",
      "node_id" : "MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDc2NTAzNjc0NQ==",
      "performed_via_github_app" : null,
      "updated_at" : "2021-01-22T00:46:47Z",
      "url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/comments/765036745",
